snippet.textDisplay:
WoW! Such a beautiful medley of Bangla and Hajong songs. This is the true beauty of Bangladesh. We have so many languages with diversified culture in such a small country and this song has represented that. Such an amazing gift for all Bangladeshi people on the month of International Mother Language Day.  We want more medleys of other tribal and regional language songs with Bangla songs like this one in upcoming episodes. Eagerly waiting!! 

Nasek Nasek Hapal Gila...
Khilabo Aaji Amra... 

#KhelaHobe
